Package: statedist
Title: Visualise State Distributions in HMMs
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jan-Ole", "Koslik", , "jan-ole.koslik@uni-bielefeld.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0004-1556-9053")),
    person("Maya", "Vienken", role = "aut"))
Description: Hidden Markov models whose state processes are driven by covariates are widely used in many fields. This package provides functions to visualise the state distributions of such models. The package is designed to work seamlessly with many popular R packages for HMMs.
